---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Story | Spearings Butchers"
  description="The Spearings family story - from a single shop on Cross Street in 1945 to 80 years serving Macclesfield with quality meat and famous pies."
  path="/our-story"
>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container page-hero-inner">
        <div class="page-hero-copy stack reveal-left">
          <div class="page-hero-badge">
            <span class="badge-year">1945</span>
            <span>Macclesfield since 1945</span>
          </div>
          <h1>A family name, <em>woven into Macclesfield</em></h1>
          <p class="body-lead">
            Founded by Denis William Spearing and his wife Margaret, Spearings has been part
            of this town for 80 years. Four generations later, the values haven't changed:
            honest produce, proper craft, and real relationships with every customer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="page-visual reveal-right reveal-d1">
          <div class="page-image-frame history">
            <img src="/images/shopfront-history.png" alt="Historic Spearings shopfront" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-cream">
      <div class="container split-grid">
        <div class="stack reveal-left">
          <p class="eyebrow">Our Heritage</p>
          <h2>From £100 and a single counter.</h2>
          <p class="body-lead">
            Denis returned from the Second World War - he'd served in the elite Airborne Division,
            parachuting into France as part of the Red Berets - and put down £100 to open a
            butcher's shop on Cross Street. That single counter became a cornerstone of Macclesfield.
          </p>
          <p>
            The family soon expanded to farming their own livestock at Kinderfield's Farm in
            Sutton, bringing a true farm-to-counter approach that remains at the heart of the
            business today.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="story-pull">
            <p>
              "The good news is I've finally had a Spearings pork pie and I'm happier than I have
              any right to be."
            </p>
            <footer>Local customer</footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-photo reveal-right reveal-d1">
          <img src="/images/denis-portrait.png" alt="Portrait of Denis Spearing" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-dark story-timeline">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal-up">
          <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-gold">Timeline</p>
          <h2>80 years of Spearings.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-list timeline-stage">
          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">1945</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>Denis and Margaret open the first shop</h3>
              <p>
                With £100 and a passion for quality, Denis opens a butcher's shop on Cross Street
                after returning from service in the Airborne Division.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">1950s</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>The family starts farming</h3>
              <p>
                The Spearings begin raising their own livestock at Kinderfield's Farm in Sutton,
                cementing the farm-to-counter quality the shop is known for.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">1987</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>Marshall takes over at Park Green</h3>
              <p>
                After training at Blackpool Food Technical College and running his own shop on
                Church Street, Marshall purchases the Park Green premises from his parents.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">2017</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>The family rallies together</h3>
              <p>
                When Marshall is diagnosed with acute Myeloid Leukaemia, his wife and daughters
                Rachael, Sarah, and Emma step in to keep the business going. They form Spearings
                Limited and carry the family name into its fourth generation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>Remembering Marshall</h3>
              <p>
                After a courageous fight and a successful bone marrow transplant in 2018 that
                brought him back to the counter he loved, Marshall sadly passed away in 2021.
                His legacy lives on in every part of the business his family continues to run.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item timeline-step" data-timeline-step>
            <div class="timeline-marker">
              <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
              <div class="timeline-year">Today</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-copy">
              <h3>80 years and still going strong</h3>
              <p>
                Still family-run, still at 12 Park Green, and still making the pies, sourcing
                the meat, and giving the service that Macclesfield has trusted for eight decades.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-tribute">
      <div class="container tribute-block">
        <div class="tribute-rule"></div>
        <p class="eyebrow">In Memory</p>
        <h2>Marshall Spearing</h2>
        <div class="tribute-portrait">
          <img src="/images/marshall.jpg" alt="Marshall Spearing in the shop" />
        </div>
        <p class="tribute-text">
          A devoted family man, a respected butcher, and a true Macclesfield legend. Marshall's
          passion for serving his community with the very best never wavered - even in his final
          days, you couldn't keep him out of the shop. His spirit is in everything we do, and
          his standards are the ones we hold ourselves to every single day.
        </p>
        <div class="tribute-rule"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-cream">
      <div class="container feature-split">
        <div class="feature-photo reveal-left">
          <img src="/images/family-team.png" alt="The Spearings family team together in the shop" />
        </div>

        <div class="stack reveal-right reveal-d1">
          <p class="eyebrow">Spearings Today</p>
          <h2>Still a warm, family-run shop.</h2>
          <p>
            The people behind the counter matter just as much as the produce on display. Pop in
            and you'll find the same warmth, the same care, and the same family commitment to
            doing things properly that's been here since 1945.
          </p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li>Family-run and rooted in Macclesfield for 80 years</li>
            <li>Produce sourced locally with provenance you can trust</li>
            <li>Famous for pies, quality meat, and personal service</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-image-frame {
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .page-image-frame img {
    border-radius: 0;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .feature-photo {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-photo img {
    border-radius: 0;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .section-tribute {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .story-timeline {
    padding: clamp(2.75rem, 5vw, 4.25rem) 0;
  }

  .story-timeline .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-list {
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-item {
    align-items: start;
    padding: 0 0 1rem;
    border-bottom: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(48px) scale(0.98);
    transition:
      opacity 0.7s ease,
      transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-step.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
  }

  .timeline-stage {
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-stage::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 4.25rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    bottom: 0.5rem;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(240, 201, 111, 0.65), rgba(240, 201, 111, 0.08));
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    justify-items: start;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 3.7rem;
    top: 0.8rem;
    width: 1.1rem;
    height: 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #f7d37b 0%, #c99a1a 70%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(201, 154, 26, 0.12), 0 0 28px rgba(201, 154, 26, 0.42);
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-year {
    color: #f0c96f;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-copy h3 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-copy {
    padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid rgba(240, 201, 111, 0.14);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 46px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .story-timeline .timeline-copy p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
    font-size: 1.16rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .tribute-block {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .tribute-block h2 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .tribute-portrait {
    max-width: 18rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
  }

  .tribute-portrait img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .tribute-text {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .tribute-rule {
    width: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #c8a96e, transparent);
    margin: 1.5rem auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .timeline-stage::before {
      left: 0.65rem;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .timeline-dot {
      left: 0.1rem;
      top: 0.65rem;
    }

    .story-timeline .timeline-copy {
      padding: 1.15rem 1.15rem 1.15rem 1.35rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  (() => {
    const steps = document.querySelectorAll('[data-timeline-step]');
    if (!steps.length) return;

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      (entries) => {
        entries.forEach((entry) => {
          if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
          entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        });
      },
      { threshold: 0.18, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' },
    );

    steps.forEach((step, index) => {
      step.style.transitionDelay = `${index * 120}ms`;
      observer.observe(step);
    });
  })();
</script>
